OL,6,FThe draft legislation originally did
OL,7,Fnot cover Northern Ireland, but the
OL,8,Fregion was added to the Bill shortly
OL,9,Fbefore it was passed by MPs in May.
OL,11,FOfficials believe there were 26
OL,12,Fsubpostmasters and subpostmistresses
OL,13,Fin Northern Ireland who received
OL,14,Fwrongful convictions linked to the
OL,15,Ffaulty IT system.
