OL,3,CLetters issued confirming quashing of
OL,4,CHorizon IT linked convictions
OL,6,FMore than 700 people who ran Post
OL,7,FOffices in the UK were prosecuted by
OL,8,Fthe company and handed criminal
OL,9,Fconvictions between 1999 and 2015 as
OL,10,FFujitsu's faulty Horizon IT system
OL,11,Fmade it appear as though money was
OL,12,Fmissing at their branches.
OL,14,FThe Post Office (Horizon System) Act
OL,15,F2024 is to exonerate those convicted
OL,16,Fon the basis of the faulty Horizon
OL,17,Faccounting software.
