OL,3,CLetters issued confirming quashing of
OL,4,CHorizon IT linked convictions
OL,6,FMadden and Finucane solicitors in
OL,7,FBelfast said four of its clients had
OL,8,Fnow received letters from the
OL,9,FDepartment of Justice confirming their
OL,10,Fconvictions had been quashed.
OL,12,FSolicitor Michael Madden said: "We are
OL,13,Fdelighted that four of our clients
OL,14,Fhave had their convictions quashed
OL,15,Fafter instructing us to challenge
OL,16,Ftheir Post Office Horizon convictions.
OL,18,F"The convictions ruined the lives of
OL,19,Fmy clients, including that of a woman
OL,20,Fwho received an eighteen month
OL,21,Fsuspended custodial sentence.
