OL,3,CLetters issued confirming quashing of
OL,4,CHorizon IT linked convictions
OL,6,F"We look forward to applying for
OL,7,Fimmediate redress under the new
OL,8,FHorizon Convictions Redress Scheme on
OL,9,Fbehalf of our clients.
OL,11,F"We continue to work with the DOJ in
OL,12,Frespect of more clients who are still
OL,13,Fwaiting for the DOJ to complete their
OL,14,Fprocess of identifying convictions
OL,15,Fthat have been quashed by the new Act."
OL,17,FFormer Portstewart sub-postmaster Lee
OL,18,FWilliamson was one of those to receive
OL,19,Fthe letters.
